# Bookeeping record rule
Every transaction (1 control) handle their own balance transaction

id ---> transaction per unit time (datetime)
|--- form ---> source of transaction (sales, transaction, payment, receipt, inventory, purchase, etc ...)
     |--- control ---> control id (every line of transaction)